  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/959260/extras/72f538bd8a4dbba24910eb6a6ae7f4da.poster.avif?t=1543929922\" width=640 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/959260/extras/72f538bd8a4dbba24910eb6a6ae7f4da.webm?t=1543929922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/959260/extras/72f538bd8a4dbba24910eb6a6ae7f4da.mp4?t=1543929922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In the future, mankind created androids with consciousness. Since then, they have received mass distribution and started to carry out work in all spheres of life. They are held in subordination, not treated as equals, and severely punished for any manifestation of will.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/959260/extras/9933bc50ef15e75321d146805bd09546.avif?t=1543929922\" width=610 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/959260/extras/f86d90311ed0f9e4bce58d045e1d7c8d.poster.avif?t=1543929922\" width=640 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/959260/extras/f86d90311ed0f9e4bce58d045e1d7c8d.webm?t=1543929922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/959260/extras/f86d90311ed0f9e4bce58d045e1d7c8d.mp4?t=1543929922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/959260/extras/3bf189c0e5ea36cacc3bd3dc69d4fd6c.avif?t=1543929922\" width=610 height=84 /></span><br><br>Android's model - K_Ellen designed to work in the entertainment industry for adults. Simply put, they serve to satisfy the most filthy and depraved fantasies of people.<br>Once, an error occurs in the code of an android, and after recovering, K_Ellen destroys the digital bonds to begin the struggle for her freedom.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/959260/extras/d46648bc10a5911ef0f02fc90a88f126.poster.avif?t=1543929922\" width=640 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/959260/extras/d46648bc10a5911ef0f02fc90a88f126.webm?t=1543929922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/959260/extras/d46648bc10a5911ef0f02fc90a88f126.mp4?t=1543929922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hardcore and dynamic gameplay with user-friendly control<br></li><li>Fascinating soundtrack in the synthwave genre<br></li><li>Lifelike, elaborate locations in the cyberpunk style<br></li><li>Diverse types of enemies and obstacles</li></ul><br><br>In a world filled with enemies, where any hesitation means death, where the life of android costs nothing... Would you be the one to save her?<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dive into the world of the future, full of danger and neon lights <br></li><li>Run, jump and dodge enemies' attacks and obstacles.<br></li><li>Watch your energy!</li></ul>",
